query:
SELECT u.id as userId, u.email, u.name, u.accountType, s.id as supplierId, s.companyName, su.id as linkId
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN supplierUsers su ON u.id = su.userId 
LEFT JOIN suppliers s ON su.supplierId = s.id 
WHERE u.email = 'apvirldtxuxegywado@nesopf.com';
